PN,38301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1774102277
OL,3,CAirline cancels flights over next six
OL,4,Cdays due to 'pilot absence'
OL,6,FThe airline Aurigny has cancelled some
OL,7,Fflights over the next six days due to
OL,8,Fstaff sickness and a lack of crew at
OL,9,FSkybus, which runs the services.
OL,11,FThe Guernsey States-owned operator
OL,12,Fsays its Alderney-Southampton and
OL,13,FAlderney-Guernsey routes will be
OL,14,Fdisrupted from Saturday 21 to Thursday
OL,15,F26 March.
OL,17,FAurigny says all affected passengers
OL,18,Fare being emailed alternative options
OL,19,Fand there is no need to contact the
OL,20,Fairline directly.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1774102277
OL,3,CAirline cancels flights over next six
OL,4,Cdays due to 'pilot absence'
OL,6,FIt also states that the "unforeseen
OL,7,Fpilot absence at Skybus ... is the
OL,8,Fsole cause of the disruption".
OL,10,FSkybus is contracted by Aurigny to
OL,11,Foperate its services to and from
OL,12,FAlderney.
OL,14,FJonathan Hinkles, Managing Director at
OL,15,FSkybus, adds in a statement: "I would
OL,16,Flike to apologise unreservedly for the
OL,17,Finconvenience caused to the community
OL,18,Fin Alderney.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1774102277
OL,3,CAirline cancels flights over next six
OL,4,Cdays due to 'pilot absence'
OL,6,F"We care deeply about this mission and
OL,7,Funderstand the importance of
OL,8,Fdelivering vital lifeline services to
OL,9,Fisland communities - and we recognise
OL,10,Fthis falls short of what is expected.
OL,12,F"We are doing everything we can to
OL,13,Fcomplete flight training for crews
OL,14,Fdedicated to Aurigny's Twin Otter
OL,15,Fservices, which will build appropriate
OL,16,Fresilience for Alderney's connectivity
OL,17,Flong into the future."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
