OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1774102277
OL,3,CAirline cancels flights over next six
OL,4,Cdays due to 'pilot absence'
OL,6,FPhilip Saunders, Chief Commercial
OL,7,FOfficer at Aurigny, explains: "As the
OL,8,Fcommunity would expect, we are working
OL,9,Fclosely with Skybus at this time to
OL,10,Fensure that services meet the
OL,11,Fstandards our communities deserve.
OL,13,F"Our dedicated customer services team
OL,14,Fare on hand to provide all the support
OL,15,Fyou would expect with amending
OL,16,Fitineraries as required."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
